channel.title: Comments on: You Don’t Know Your Impact Until You Do.
channel.description: iteration, making, building, and coding in education

item.title: By: Barbara Fox
item.dc:creator: Barbara Fox
item.description: It doesn't have to come from many students, but these gifts of affirmation are the fuel for the passion teachers/guides bring to the work every day. Continue to believe in your students and yourself. You have a "proud Papa" singing your praises in Cleveland.
